participant "Reservations" as Res [[/microservices/svc-reservations/]] #FFF8F0
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #FCE4EC

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-partner-integrations.html#/Partner%20Bookings/createPartnerBooking View in Swagger UI]]
