activate TC #DBEAFE
TC --> Svc : OK
deactivate TC

Svc -> Res : [[/microservices/svc-reservations/#post-reservations-create-a-new-reservation Create reservation]]
activate Res #DBEAFE
Res --> Svc : OK
deactivate Res

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FCE4EC
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

